# textdomain: mcl_dripstone
Dripstone block=Bloco de estalactite
Dripstone is type of stone that allows stalagmites and stalagtites to grow on it=Espeleotema é um tipo de rocha que permite o crescimento de estalagmites e estalactites dele
Pointed dripstone=Espeleotema pontiagudo
Pointed dripstone is what stalagmites and stalagtites are made of=O espeleotema pontiagudo é o que forma as estalagmites e estalactites
Pointed dripstone (@1/@2)=Espeleotema pontiagudo (@1/@2)
